### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ==========================================
### CLIENTES
### ==========================================

### Crear cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/client
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Construcciones García S.L.",
  "cif": "B12345678",
  "email": "garcia@empresa.com",
  "phone": "912345678",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Mayor",
    "number": "15",
    "postal": "28001",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

### Listar clientes (con paginación)
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar clientes (con filtro por nombre)
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?name=García
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener un cliente concreto
GET {{baseUrl}}/client/ID_DEL_CLIENTE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar cliente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/client/ID_DEL_CLIENTE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Construcciones García Renovado S.L.",
  "phone": "911222333"
}

### Archivar cliente (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/client/ID_DEL_CLIENTE?soft=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Eliminar cliente (hard delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/client/ID_DEL_CLIENTE?soft=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar clientes archivados
GET {{baseUrl}}/client/archived
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Restaurar cliente archivado
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/client/ID_DEL_CLIENTE/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
